title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – May 3 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – May 3 2022
description:
Mayor Adams makes fool of himself at Met Gala, wears "End Gun Violence" tuxedo. The Democrat plan is treachery. The one-and-only Bill O'Reilly joins Buck to opine on the abortion leak, the midterms, Eric Adams and the nationwide crime wave -- and his new book: "Killing the Killers: The Secret War Against Terrorists." Buck's history podcasts. Buck takes calls. Donald Trump's 2016 victory could end up saving millions of lives.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
